main event: A report of a UFO sighting in Abilene, Texas on 29 September 1966, observed by multiple witnesses.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for one hour,The object was described as round and white with light,There were multiple witnesses including a 17-year-old gas station attendant and a 44-year-old housewife,The objects stood still before moving rapidly in different directions,No physical evidence or photographs were collected.
sighted object: one round white object with light
witness description: a 17-year-old gas station attendant and a 44-year-old housewife
